{
  "doc_id": "FC-LS",
  "source_pdf": "/Users/zwy/毕设/V7/data/raw/FC-LS.pdf",
  "page": 65,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0002",
      "text": " 46",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0003",
      "text": "more storage has become available).  The sender of the RSCN Request may coalesce several",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        540.01,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0004",
      "text": "events into a single report.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        213.17,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0005",
      "text": "A RSCN Request may be sent by the Fabric to notify registered Nx_Ports of changes detected by the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        540.0,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0006",
      "text": "Fabric.  The Fabric Controller (FFFFFDh) issues the RSCN Request to the registered Nx_Ports.  An",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        539.96,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0007",
      "text": "Nx_Port may also issue a RSCN Request to the Fabric Controller or another Nx_Port to indicate",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        539.92,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0008",
      "text": "changes of state within the Nx_Port that are not otherwise detectable by the Fabric. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        467.05,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0009",
      "text": "The Payload of a RSCN Request includes a list containing the addresses of the affected Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        539.94,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0010",
      "text": "The RSCN includes a summary indication of the type of state change being reported to assist in ana-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        540.08,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0011",
      "text": "lyzing the change.  The sending of RSCN between Nx_Ports, neither of which are the Fabric Control-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.13,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0012",
      "text": "ler, is permitted.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        167.05,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0013",
      "text": "4.2.18.2  RSCNs issued by the Fabric Controller",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        321.51,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0014",
      "text": "The Fabric Controller shall issue an RSCN Request to all registered Nx_Ports for an affected",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        539.98,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0015",
      "text": "Nx_Port when the Fabric detects an event.  The Fabric Controller shall ensure that any Fabric-provid-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.07,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0016",
      "text": "ed resources (e.g., the Name Service) have received updates to reflect changes caused by the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        539.97,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0017",
      "text": "event, prior to issuing the RSCN for the event.  An event may include any of the following:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        492.01,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0018",
      "text": "a) an implicit Fabric Logout of the affected Nx_Port, including Loss-of-Signal, NOS, and OLS, or",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        298.96,
        539.97,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0019",
      "text": "when the Fabric receives a FLOGI that contains new or different information from a port that",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        310.96,
        540.01,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0020",
      "text": "had already completed FLOGI;",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        322.96,
        258.99,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0021",
      "text": "b) a loop initialization of the affected L_Port, and the L_bit was set in the LISA Sequence;",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        346.96,
        504.61,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0022",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        370.96,
        114.34,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0023",
      "text": "a Fabric Login from an affected Nx_Port not previously logged in;",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        370.96,
        410.14,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0024",
      "text": "d) the Fabric path between the affected Nx_Port and any other Nx_Port has changed (e.g., a",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        394.96,
        540.1,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0025",
      "text": "change to the Fabric routing tables that affects the ability of the Fabric to deliver frames in or-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        406.96,
        540.01,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0026",
      "text": "der, or an E_Port initialization or failure); ",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        418.96,
        303.47,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0027",
      "text": "e) any other Fabric-detected state change of the affected Nx_Port;",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        442.96,
        404.03,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0028",
      "text": "f)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        466.96,
        112.13,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0029",
      "text": "the affected Nx_Port issues an RSCN Request to the Fabric Controller.",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        466.96,
        436.91,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0030",
      "text": "A registered Nx_Port that receives an RSCN Request may perform any operation to determine the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.0,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0031",
      "text": "nature of the state change.  These operations include the PDISC ELS, the ADISC ELS, a query to the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.98,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0032",
      "text": "Name Service, or a ULP query.  The Fabric may accumulate affected Nx_Port addresses for subse-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.09,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0033",
      "text": "quent delivery to reduce the volume of RSCN traffic.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        326.51,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0034",
      "text": "4.2.18.3  RSCN issued by the affected Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        314.81,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0035",
      "text": "An Nx_Port shall issue an RSCN Request to the Fabric Controller or the Nx_Port that has registered",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.89,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0036",
      "text": "for receipt of RSCN Requests or both when an event is detected by an Nx_Port.  Fabric Controllers",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.01,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0037",
      "text": "are implicitly registered to receive RSCNs after a successful implicit or explicit FLOGI.  Nx_Ports, nei-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        539.95,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0038",
      "text": "ther of which are the Fabric Controller, that request RSCNs are hereafter called registered Nx_Ports.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.93,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0039",
      "text": "Unless it is providing a service associated with a well known address an Nx_Port shall only issue",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.94,
        634.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0040",
      "text": "RSCNs with an event qualifier of 2h or 0h.  An event may include any of the following:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        474.2,
        646.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0041",
      "text": "a) a failure within the affected Nx_Port;",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        659.02,
        282.97,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p065_s0042",
      "text": "b) any other important state change of the affected Nx_Port (e.g., an event defined by a FC-4).",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        683.02,
        528.51,
        694.13
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}